tempsense  
Basic temperature sensor providing current, max, and min Fahrenheit temperature values across a serial link and to an LCD.  Using the LiquidCrystal display library to output to a 16x2 LCD display with a Hitachi HD44780 driver.  

The circuit: 
* Temperature sensor attached to analog pin 0 
* LCD RS pin to digital pin 12 
* LCD Enable pin to digital pin 11 
* LCD D4 pin to digital pin 5 
* LCD D5 pin to digital pin 4 
* LCD D6 pin to digital pin 3 
* LCD D7 pin to digital pin 2 
* LCD R/W pin to ground  

created 19 March 2011 
by Peter Gebhard